@startuml sd_OperationLogService_getLogs
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title OperationLogService.getLogs(pageable) - 分页查询操作日志

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "SystemController" as Ctrl
participant "OperationLogService" as LogSvc
participant "OperationLogRepository" as LogRepo
participant "Page" as Page

Client -> Ctrl: GET /api/system/logs?page=0&size=20
Ctrl -> LogSvc: getLogs(pageable)
LogSvc -> LogRepo: findAllByOrderByCreateTimeDesc(pageable)
note right of LogSvc : 按createTime降序\n最新操作排在前面
LogRepo --> LogSvc: Page<OperationLog>
LogSvc --> Ctrl: Page<OperationLog>
note right of Page : 含content/totalPages\ntotalElements/number
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse<Page>\n[ {username:admin, operation:工资计算,\n   result:SUCCESS, createTime:...}, ... ]
@enduml
